    <text>
    <body>
        <p>Organized at Paris, Kentucky under Colonel Leonidas Metcalfe. Fought in a number of battles, including battle of Big Hill, Kentucky. Suffered great losses during that initial battle. Metcalfe resigned after battle of Big Hill, Kentucky, replaced by Col. Faulkner. Later fought at Macon and at Nashville, Tennessee. Regiment mustered out on 10 Jul 1865.</p>

